        {
            "title": "南海爭議︱菲律賓飛機闖黃岩島領空  解放軍：追蹤監視警告驅離",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"南海黃岩島一直有主權爭議。美聯社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/aab7c7416548084b127b26c92a8db576/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250218/_2025021817503816174.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">南海黃岩島一直有主權爭議。美聯社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>央視新聞報道，解放軍南部戰區新聞發言人田軍里空軍大校表示，今日（18日），菲律賓1架C-208型機未經中國政府允許，非法闖入中國黃岩島領空，還顛倒非黑白，散佈假敘事。中國人民解放軍南部戰區組織海空兵力，依法依規追蹤監視、警告驅離。菲方行為嚴重侵害中國主權，嚴重違反國際法和中國法律相關規定。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"菲律賓海軍的C-208型飛機。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0bc41387c1cf71972c940610ca5fb4c2/2024-12/1221030.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        菲律賓海軍的C-208型飛機。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3412786/\">中國海警驅離進入黃岩島空域菲律賓飛機</a></strong><br/>\n<br/>\n田軍里強調，黃岩島是中國固有領土，菲方妄圖以軍事挑釁謀求其非法主權主張、以煽宣炒作誤導國際認知，注定是徒勞無功的。戰區部隊保持高度戒備，堅決捍衛國家主權安全和南海地區和平穩定。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053530/即時-中國-南海爭議︱菲律賓飛機闖黃岩島領空-解放軍-追蹤監視警告驅離",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-18 17:56:10",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "TVB新春團拜｜曾志偉狂摸獅頭圖沾好運 港姐王汛文 倪樂琳 楊梓瑤對𢭃利是成績感滿意",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/335cac05fb80b8b71c431f1921f95def/2025-02/page_240.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/40dbaa00eddc71ef98064177d1c10102/3f214048a8904f328571b40ec814d385-4d923e2320a440000831d2b850c3adfc-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b4579ae173b\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b4579ae173c\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"TVB新春團拜｜曾志偉狂摸獅頭圖沾好運 港姐王汛文 倪樂琳 楊梓瑤對𢭃利是成績感滿意\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/773e9ebcaf58beff9ff12f9a30a14b61/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250218/_2025021817392468868.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">TVB新春團拜｜曾志偉狂摸獅頭圖沾好運 港姐王汛文 倪樂琳 楊梓瑤對𢭃利是成績感滿意</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>「無綫乙巳年新春團拜嘉年華」今日（18日）在電視城舉行，電視廣播有限公司行政主席許濤，多位高級行政人員包括曾志偉、曾勵珍、樂易玲、蕭世和等以及應屆港姐冠軍倪樂琳、季軍楊梓瑤和友誼小姐王汛文出席。許濤在新春致辭時表示TVB的力量來自各位同事的團結，面對市場逆境和挑戰，只要團結，就會好似過去57年一樣，繼續創造許多輝煌。許濤隨後與曾志偉、蕭世和為醒獅點睛，與一眾同事欣賞醒獅表演，又向同事派朱古力金幣，眾人不時摸獅頭沾好運，場面熱鬧。\n\n</p><h2>團結就是力量</h2>\n<p>三位港姐受訪時表示有狂摸醒獅，望發財以及事業順利，楊梓瑤笑指今年利是特別多，指以往在北京過年時，當地不流行派利是，今年在香港就有4位數字利是，會先儲起來，會不會用來買包包？她坦言幾千元不夠，想買的包包要10幾萬，笑指要儲利是錢儲到60歲才買到，又說過年時工作不多，食飽就瞓，瞓飽就食，自爆肥了4公斤，要做運動減肥和戒食零食。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088387/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"TVB行政主席許濤，多位高級行政人員曾志偉、曾勵珍等出席「無綫乙巳年新春團拜嘉年華」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8dd5c313f88678f2c24862efd1ea7b80/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_54_55_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        TVB行政主席許濤，多位高級行政人員曾志偉、曾勵珍等出席「無綫乙巳年新春團拜嘉年華」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088388/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"左起︰友誼小姐王汛文、港姐冠軍倪樂琳、季軍楊梓瑤。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9eb80353a4ff3b798d9a1b54dfc5fb97/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_54_55_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        左起︰友誼小姐王汛文、港姐冠軍倪樂琳、季軍楊梓瑤。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088391/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉與許濤一同事欣賞醒獅表演。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0570ab5d23c6e62f667ebf89078879f/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_54_56_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉與許濤一同事欣賞醒獅表演。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088395/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"電視廣播有限公司行政主席許濤表示團結就是力量。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb9c1c543a99d6c29d5db5f97c25139f/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_54_57_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        電視廣播有限公司行政主席許濤表示團結就是力量。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088401/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉為醒獅點睛。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d5e359f7722f3c416daf02d57080d651/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_54_59_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉為醒獅點睛。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088403/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樂易玲與友誼小姐王汛文，香港小姐季軍、冠軍楊梓瑤與倪樂琳。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e758c98cd2c36507dea703bf7263d47/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_55_00_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樂易玲與友誼小姐王汛文，香港小姐季軍、冠軍楊梓瑤與倪樂琳。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4088404/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉不時摸獅頭沾好運。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/551a9b8758e0d2d42b830537ac27d4a6/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-18_at_14_55_00_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉不時摸獅頭沾好運。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>楊梓瑤靠自己買貴價包包</h2>\n<p>倪樂琳和王汛文都說有4位數字利是，倪樂琳笑指小時候的利是錢多達5位數字，長大後媽媽就叫親友不用給她利是，故利是錢少了很多。她透露新年後會多出席慈善餐舞會，趁機識男仔？她笑言不是抱識男仔心態出席活動，民以食為天當然以吃為主，同時表示𠰻類活動上常有城大校友和她打招呼。楊梓瑤就表示不需要男性送包包？她說：「我要靠自己，用自己賺的錢買，有成就感。」倪樂琳聞言即心心眼向她表示「買包包送給朋友更有成就感」，十分好笑。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053525/即時-娛樂-TVB新春團拜-曾志偉狂摸獅頭圖沾好運-港姐王汛文-倪樂琳-楊梓瑤對𢭃利是成績感滿意",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-18 17:51:16",
